abstract: President Obama and Hillary Rodham Clinton share a private lunch; meeting is acknowledged only after People magazine posts on Twitter about it; lunch is more evidence that Clinton is continuing close relationship with Obama as speculation about her plans for 2016 presidential election grows louder.
lead_paragraph: President Obama and Hillary Rodham Clinton shared a private lunch, a meeting that was acknowledged only after People magazine posted on Twitter about it.

headline.main: Clinton-Obama Lunch Hints at Continuing and Close Ties
headline.print_headline: Clinton-Obama Lunch Hints at Continuing and Close Ties
